{"tha-ap63:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap63:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap63:0.3":"1 Sakacintaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap63:1.1":"“Pavanam kananam disva, ","tha-ap63:1.2":"appasaddamanavilam; ","tha-ap63:1.3":"Isinam anucinnamva, ","tha-ap63:1.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap63:2.1":"Thupam katvana pulinam, ","tha-ap63:2.2":"nanapuppham samokirim; ","tha-ap63:2.3":"Sammukha viya sambuddham, ","tha-ap63:2.4":"nimmitam abhivandaham. ","tha-ap63:3.1":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap63:3.2":"raja ratthamhi issaro; ","tha-ap63:3.3":"Sakakammabhiraddhoham, ","tha-ap63:3.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap63:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap63:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap63:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap63:4.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap63:5.1":"Asitikappenantayaso, ","tha-ap63:5.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap63:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap63:5.4":"catudipamhi issaro. ","tha-ap63:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap63:6.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap63:6.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap63:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap63:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sakacintaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap63:8.1":"Sakacintaniyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}